{"tid":1399244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孫子兵法","createTime":"2019-08-03T05:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T06:04:20.000Z","uid":55951,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03fd3a12e8bb489ebbc8a9898fbe7144b9f90756","tid":1399244,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"出其所不趨，趨其所不意。行千里而不勞之者，行於無人之地也。攻而必取者，攻其所不守也。守而必固者，守其所不攻也。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac188641d2c3ed134d3479a8b7f02c30a941f8c9","tid":1399244,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"中國殿堂級兵法大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}